Package: sotto
Version: @VERSION@
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Pratik Sancheti <psancheti6666@gmail.com>
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/psancheti6666/sotto
Depends: acl, openssl, pkexec | policykit-1, zenity | kdialog, libnotify-bin, pulseaudio-utils, xdotool, x11-utils, xclip, wl-clipboard, ydotool
Recommends: wtype, gir1.2-ayatanaappindicator3-0.1
Description: Private, local-first dictation
 Hold a key, speak naturally, release — cleaned, punctuated text is typed at
 your cursor in any app. Speech recognition and cleanup run entirely on your
 own machine; nothing is sent to the cloud. The AI models (~3-4 GB) download
 themselves on first launch. No account, no subscription.
